The last equality is due to the fact that \begin<<7968>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<7968>>$<<3173>>\begin<<13650>>tex2html_deferred<<13650>>\bf\end<<13651>>tex2html_deferred<<13651>>d<<3173>>_i$\end<<7969>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<7969>>\space and \begin<<7970>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<7970>>$<<3174>>\begin<<13652>>tex2html_deferred<<13652>>\bf\end<<13653>>tex2html_deferred<<13653>>d<<3174>>_j$\end<<7971>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<7971>>
are A-orthogonal, i.e., \begin<<7972>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<7972>>$<<3175>>\begin<<13654>>tex2html_deferred<<13654>>\bf\end<<13655>>tex2html_deferred<<13655>>d<<3175>>^T_i<<3176>>\begin<<13656>>tex2html_deferred<<13656>>\bf\end<<13657>>tex2html_deferred<<13657>>A<<3176>><<3177>>\begin<<13658>>tex2html_deferred<<13658>>\bf\end<<13659>>tex2html_deferred<<13659>>d<<3177>>_j=0$\end<<7973>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<7973>>.
Substituting this into Eq. (\ref<<3178>>CGerror<<3178>>) we get
\begin<<3179>>equation<<3179>> 
  <<3180>>\begin<<13660>>tex2html_deferred<<13660>>\bf\end<<13661>>tex2html_deferred<<13661>>e<<3180>>_<<3181>>n+1<<3181>>=<<3182>>\begin<<13662>>tex2html_deferred<<13662>>\bf\end<<13663>>tex2html_deferred<<13663>>e<<3182>>_n+\delta_n<<3183>>\begin<<13664>>tex2html_deferred<<13664>>\bf\end<<13665>>tex2html_deferred<<13665>>d<<3183>>_n
  =<<3184>>\begin<<13666>>tex2html_deferred<<13666>>\bf\end<<13667>>tex2html_deferred<<13667>>e<<3184>>_n-\left(\frac<<6689>><<3185>>\begin<<13668>>tex2html_deferred<<13668>>\bf\end<<13669>>tex2html_deferred<<13669>>d<<3185>>_n^T<<3186>>\begin<<13670>>tex2html_deferred<<13670>>\bf\end<<13671>>tex2html_deferred<<13671>>A<<3186>><<3187>>\begin<<13672>>tex2html_deferred<<13672>>\bf\end<<13673>>tex2html_deferred<<13673>>e<<3187>>_0<<6689>><<6690>><<3188>>\begin<<13674>>tex2html_deferred<<13674>>\bf\end<<13675>>tex2html_deferred<<13675>>d<<3188>>_n^T<<3189>>\begin<<13676>>tex2html_deferred<<13676>>\bf\end<<13677>>tex2html_deferred<<13677>>A<<3189>><<3190>>\begin<<13678>>tex2html_deferred<<13678>>\bf\end<<13679>>tex2html_deferred<<13679>>d<<3190>>_n<<6690>>\right)<<3191>>\begin<<13680>>tex2html_deferred<<13680>>\bf\end<<13681>>tex2html_deferred<<13681>>d<<3191>>_n
\end<<3192>>equation<<3192>>
\begin<<13682>>tex2html_deferred<<13682>>\par\end<<13683>>tex2html_deferred<<13683>>
On the other hand, we represent the error \begin<<7974>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<7974>>$<<3193>>\begin<<13684>>tex2html_deferred<<13684>>\bf\end<<13685>>tex2html_deferred<<13685>>e<<3193>>_0=<<3194>>\begin<<13686>>tex2html_deferred<<13686>>\bf\end<<13687>>tex2html_deferred<<13687>>x<<3194>>_0-<<3195>>\begin<<13688>>tex2html_deferred<<13688>>\bf\end<<13689>>tex2html_deferred<<13689>>x<<3195>>^*$\end<<7975>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<7975>> 
associated with the initial guess \begin<<7976>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<7976>>$<<3196>>\begin<<13690>>tex2html_deferred<<13690>>\bf\end<<13691>>tex2html_deferred<<13691>>x<<3196>>_0$\end<<7977>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<7977>>\space as a linear combination of 
the search vectors \begin<<7978>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<7978>>$\{<<3197>>\begin<<13692>>tex2html_deferred<<13692>>\bf\end<<13693>>tex2html_deferred<<13693>>d<<3197>>_0,\cdots,<<3198>>\begin<<13694>>tex2html_deferred<<13694>>\bf\end<<13695>>tex2html_deferred<<13695>>d<<3198>>_<<3199>>N-1<<3199>>\}$\end<<7979>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<7979>>\space treated as \begin<<7980>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<7980>>$N$\end<<7981>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<7981>>\space basis 
vectors that span the N-D vector space:
\begin<<3200>>equation<<3200>>
  <<3201>>\begin<<13696>>tex2html_deferred<<13696>>\bf\end<<13697>>tex2html_deferred<<13697>>e<<3201>>_0=\sum_<<3202>>i=0<<3202>>^<<3203>>N-1<<3203>> c_i<<3204>>\begin<<13698>>tex2html_deferred<<13698>>\bf\end<<13699>>tex2html_deferred<<13699>>d<<3204>>_i
  =\sum_<<3205>>i=0<<3205>>^<<3206>>N-1<<3206>><<3207>>\begin<<13700>>tex2html_deferred<<13700>>\bf\end<<13701>>tex2html_deferred<<13701>>p<<3207>>_<<6691>><<3208>>\begin<<13702>>tex2html_deferred<<13702>>\bf\end<<13703>>tex2html_deferred<<13703>>d<<3208>>_i<<6691>>(<<3209>>\begin<<13704>>tex2html_deferred<<13704>>\bf\end<<13705>>tex2html_deferred<<13705>>e<<3209>>_0) 
  =\sum_<<3210>>i=0<<3210>>^<<3211>>N-1<<3211>> \left(\frac<<6692>> <<3212>>\begin<<13706>>tex2html_deferred<<13706>>\bf\end<<13707>>tex2html_deferred<<13707>>d<<3212>>^T_i<<3213>>\begin<<13708>>tex2html_deferred<<13708>>\bf\end<<13709>>tex2html_deferred<<13709>>A<<3213>><<3214>>\begin<<13710>>tex2html_deferred<<13710>>\bf\end<<13711>>tex2html_deferred<<13711>>e<<3214>>_0<<6692>><<6693>> <<3215>>\begin<<13712>>tex2html_deferred<<13712>>\bf\end<<13713>>tex2html_deferred<<13713>>d<<3215>>^T_i<<3216>>\begin<<13714>>tex2html_deferred<<13714>>\bf\end<<13715>>tex2html_deferred<<13715>>A<<3216>><<3217>>\begin<<13716>>tex2html_deferred<<13716>>\bf\end<<13717>>tex2html_deferred<<13717>>d<<3217>>_i<<6693>>\right)<<3218>>\begin<<13718>>tex2html_deferred<<13718>>\bf\end<<13719>>tex2html_deferred<<13719>>d<<3218>>_i
  \label<<3219>>cine0<<3219>>
\end<<3220>>equation<<3220>>
where \begin<<7982>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<7982>>$<<3221>>\begin<<13720>>tex2html_deferred<<13720>>\bf\end<<13721>>tex2html_deferred<<13721>>p<<3221>>_<<6694>><<3222>>\begin<<13722>>tex2html_deferred<<13722>>\bf\end<<13723>>tex2html_deferred<<13723>>d<<3222>>_i<<6694>>(<<3223>>\begin<<13724>>tex2html_deferred<<13724>>\bf\end<<13725>>tex2html_deferred<<13725>>e<<3223>>_0)$\end<<7983>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<7983>>\space is the A-projection of \begin<<7984>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<7984>>$<<3224>>\begin<<13726>>tex2html_deferred<<13726>>\bf\end<<13727>>tex2html_deferred<<13727>>e<<3224>>_0$\end<<7985>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<7985>> 
onto the ith basis vector \begin<<7986>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<7986>>$<<3225>>\begin<<13728>>tex2html_deferred<<13728>>\bf\end<<13729>>tex2html_deferred<<13729>>d<<3225>>_i$\end<<7987>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<7987>>:
\begin<<3226>>equation<<3226>>
  <<3227>>\begin<<13730>>tex2html_deferred<<13730>>\bf\end<<13731>>tex2html_deferred<<13731>>p<<3227>>_<<6695>><<3228>>\begin<<13732>>tex2html_deferred<<13732>>\bf\end<<13733>>tex2html_deferred<<13733>>d<<3228>>_i<<6695>>(<<3229>>\begin<<13734>>tex2html_deferred<<13734>>\bf\end<<13735>>tex2html_deferred<<13735>>e<<3229>>_0)=c_i<<3230>>\begin<<13736>>tex2html_deferred<<13736>>\bf\end<<13737>>tex2html_deferred<<13737>>d<<3230>>_i
  =\left(\frac<<6696>> <<3231>>\begin<<13738>>tex2html_deferred<<13738>>\bf\end<<13739>>tex2html_deferred<<13739>>d<<3231>>^T_i<<3232>>\begin<<13740>>tex2html_deferred<<13740>>\bf\end<<13741>>tex2html_deferred<<13741>>A<<3232>><<3233>>\begin<<13742>>tex2html_deferred<<13742>>\bf\end<<13743>>tex2html_deferred<<13743>>e<<3233>>_0<<6696>><<6697>> <<3234>>\begin<<13744>>tex2html_deferred<<13744>>\bf\end<<13745>>tex2html_deferred<<13745>>d<<3234>>^T_i<<3235>>\begin<<13746>>tex2html_deferred<<13746>>\bf\end<<13747>>tex2html_deferred<<13747>>A<<3235>><<3236>>\begin<<13748>>tex2html_deferred<<13748>>\bf\end<<13749>>tex2html_deferred<<13749>>d<<3236>>_i<<6697>>\right)
  <<3237>>\begin<<13750>>tex2html_deferred<<13750>>\bf\end<<13751>>tex2html_deferred<<13751>>d<<3237>>_i
\end<<3238>>equation<<3238>>
We note that the coefficient \begin<<7988>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<7988>>$c_i$\end<<7989>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<7989>>\space happens to be the negative optimal step
size in Eq. (\ref<<3239>>delta_gd<<3239>>):
\begin<<3240>>equation<<3240>>
  c_i=\frac<<6698>><<3241>>\begin<<13752>>tex2html_deferred<<13752>>\bf\end<<13753>>tex2html_deferred<<13753>>d<<3241>>^T_i<<3242>>\begin<<13754>>tex2html_deferred<<13754>>\bf\end<<13755>>tex2html_deferred<<13755>>A<<3242>><<3243>>\begin<<13756>>tex2html_deferred<<13756>>\bf\end<<13757>>tex2html_deferred<<13757>>e<<3243>>_0<<6698>><<6699>><<3244>>\begin<<13758>>tex2html_deferred<<13758>>\bf\end<<13759>>tex2html_deferred<<13759>>d<<3244>>^T_i<<3245>>\begin<<13760>>tex2html_deferred<<13760>>\bf\end<<13761>>tex2html_deferred<<13761>>A<<3245>><<3246>>\begin<<13762>>tex2html_deferred<<13762>>\bf\end<<13763>>tex2html_deferred<<13763>>d<<3246>>_i<<6699>>=-\delta_i
\end<<3247>>equation<<3247>>
Now the expression of \begin<<7990>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<7990>>$<<3248>>\begin<<13764>>tex2html_deferred<<13764>>\bf\end<<13765>>tex2html_deferred<<13765>>e<<3248>>_<<3249>>n+1<<3249>>$\end<<7991>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<7991>>\space in Eq. (\ref<<3250>>CGerror<<3250>>) can be written as
\begin<<3251>>equation<<3251>> 
  <<3252>>\begin<<13766>>tex2html_deferred<<13766>>\bf\end<<13767>>tex2html_deferred<<13767>>e<<3252>>_<<3253>>n+1<<3253>>=<<3254>>\begin<<13768>>tex2html_deferred<<13768>>\bf\end<<13769>>tex2html_deferred<<13769>>e<<3254>>_0+\sum_<<3255>>i=0<<3255>>^n\delta_i<<3256>>\begin<<13770>>tex2html_deferred<<13770>>\bf\end<<13771>>tex2html_deferred<<13771>>d<<3256>>_i
  =\sum_<<3257>>i=0<<3257>>^<<3258>>N-1<<3258>>c_i<<3259>>\begin<<13772>>tex2html_deferred<<13772>>\bf\end<<13773>>tex2html_deferred<<13773>>d<<3259>>_i-\sum_<<3260>>i=0<<3260>>^n c_i<<3261>>\begin<<13774>>tex2html_deferred<<13774>>\bf\end<<13775>>tex2html_deferred<<13775>>d<<3261>>_i=\sum_<<3262>>i=n+1<<3262>>^<<3263>>N-1<<3263>>c_i<<3264>>\begin<<13776>>tex2html_deferred<<13776>>\bf\end<<13777>>tex2html_deferred<<13777>>d<<3264>>_i
  =\sum_<<3265>>i=n+1<<3265>>^<<3266>>N-1<<3266>><<3267>>\begin<<13778>>tex2html_deferred<<13778>>\bf\end<<13779>>tex2html_deferred<<13779>>p<<3267>>_<<6700>><<3268>>\begin<<13780>>tex2html_deferred<<13780>>\bf\end<<13781>>tex2html_deferred<<13781>>d<<3268>>_i<<6700>>(<<3269>>\begin<<13782>>tex2html_deferred<<13782>>\bf\end<<13783>>tex2html_deferred<<13783>>e<<3269>>_0)
\end<<3270>>equation<<3270>>
We see that in each iteration from \begin<<7992>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<7992>>$n$\end<<7993>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<7993>>\space to \begin<<7994>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<7994>>$n+1$\end<<7995>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<7995>>, the number of terms
in the summation is reduced by one, i.e., the nth component 
\begin<<7996>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<7996>>$<<3271>>\begin<<13784>>tex2html_deferred<<13784>>\bf\end<<13785>>tex2html_deferred<<13785>>p<<3271>>_<<6701>><<3272>>\begin<<13786>>tex2html_deferred<<13786>>\bf\end<<13787>>tex2html_deferred<<13787>>d<<3272>>_n<<6701>>(<<3273>>\begin<<13788>>tex2html_deferred<<13788>>\bf\end<<13789>>tex2html_deferred<<13789>>e<<3273>>_0)$\end<<7997>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<7997>>\space of \begin<<7998>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<7998>>$<<3274>>\begin<<13790>>tex2html_deferred<<13790>>\bf\end<<13791>>tex2html_deferred<<13791>>e<<3274>>_n$\end<<7999>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<7999>>\space along the direction of 
\begin<<8000>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<8000>>$<<3275>>\begin<<13792>>tex2html_deferred<<13792>>\bf\end<<13793>>tex2html_deferred<<13793>>d<<3275>>_n$\end<<8001>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<8001>>\space is completely eliminated. After \begin<<8002>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<8002>>$N$\end<<8003>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<8003>>\space such iterations, the
error is reduced from \begin<<8004>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<8004>>$<<3276>>\begin<<13794>>tex2html_deferred<<13794>>\bf\end<<13795>>tex2html_deferred<<13795>>e<<3276>>_0$\end<<8005>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<8005>>\space to \begin<<8006>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<8006>>$<<3277>>\begin<<13796>>tex2html_deferred<<13796>>\bf\end<<13797>>tex2html_deferred<<13797>>e<<3277>>_N=<<3278>>\begin<<13798>>tex2html_deferred<<13798>>\bf\end<<13799>>tex2html_deferred<<13799>>0<<3278>>$\end<<8007>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<8007>>, and the true 
solution is obtained \begin<<8008>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<8008>>$<<3279>>\begin<<13800>>tex2html_deferred<<13800>>\bf\end<<13801>>tex2html_deferred<<13801>>x<<3279>>_N=<<3280>>\begin<<13802>>tex2html_deferred<<13802>>\bf\end<<13803>>tex2html_deferred<<13803>>x<<3280>>^*+<<3281>>\begin<<13804>>tex2html_deferred<<13804>>\bf\end<<13805>>tex2html_deferred<<13805>>e<<3281>>_N=<<3282>>\begin<<13806>>tex2html_deferred<<13806>>\bf\end<<13807>>tex2html_deferred<<13807>>x<<3282>>^*$\end<<8009>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<8009>>. 
\begin<<13808>>tex2html_deferred<<13808>>\par\end<<13809>>tex2html_deferred<<13809>>
Pre-multiplying \begin<<8010>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<8010>>$<<3283>>\begin<<13810>>tex2html_deferred<<13810>>\bf\end<<13811>>tex2html_deferred<<13811>>d<<3283>>_k^T<<3284>>\begin<<13812>>tex2html_deferred<<13812>>\bf\end<<13813>>tex2html_deferred<<13813>>A<<3284>>\;(k\le n)$\end<<8011>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<8011>>\space on both sides of the
equation above, we get:
\begin<<3285>>equation<<3285>> 
  <<3286>>\begin<<13814>>tex2html_deferred<<13814>>\bf\end<<13815>>tex2html_deferred<<13815>>d<<3286>>_k^T<<3287>>\begin<<13816>>tex2html_deferred<<13816>>\bf\end<<13817>>tex2html_deferred<<13817>>A<<3287>><<3288>>\begin<<13818>>tex2html_deferred<<13818>>\bf\end<<13819>>tex2html_deferred<<13819>>e<<3288>>_<<3289>>n+1<<3289>>=<<3290>>\begin<<13820>>tex2html_deferred<<13820>>\bf\end<<13821>>tex2html_deferred<<13821>>d<<3290>>_k^T<<3291>>\begin<<13822>>tex2html_deferred<<13822>>\bf\end<<13823>>tex2html_deferred<<13823>>g<<3291>>_<<3292>>n+1<<3292>>
  =\sum_<<3293>>i=n+1<<3293>>^<<3294>>N-1<<3294>>c_i<<3295>>\begin<<13824>>tex2html_deferred<<13824>>\bf\end<<13825>>tex2html_deferred<<13825>>d<<3295>>_k^T<<3296>>\begin<<13826>>tex2html_deferred<<13826>>\bf\end<<13827>>tex2html_deferred<<13827>>A<<3296>><<3297>>\begin<<13828>>tex2html_deferred<<13828>>\bf\end<<13829>>tex2html_deferred<<13829>>d<<3297>>_j=0 
  \label<<3298>>gd0<<3298>>
\end<<3299>>equation<<3299>>
We see that after \begin<<8012>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<8012>>$n+1$\end<<8013>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<8013>>\space iterations the remaining error \begin<<8014>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<8014>>$<<3300>>\begin<<13830>>tex2html_deferred<<13830>>\bf\end<<13831>>tex2html_deferred<<13831>>e<<3300>>_<<3301>>n+1<<3301>>$\end<<8015>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<8015>>\space is 
A-orthogonal to all previous directions \begin<<8016>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<8016>>$<<3302>>\begin<<13832>>tex2html_deferred<<13832>>\bf\end<<13833>>tex2html_deferred<<13833>>d<<3302>>_0,\cdots,<<3303>>\begin<<13834>>tex2html_deferred<<13834>>\bf\end<<13835>>tex2html_deferred<<13835>>d<<3303>>_n$\end<<8017>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<8017>>, and 
the gradient \begin<<8018>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<8018>>$<<3304>>\begin<<13836>>tex2html_deferred<<13836>>\bf\end<<13837>>tex2html_deferred<<13837>>g<<3304>>_<<3305>>n+1<<3305>>$\end<<8019>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<8019>>\space is orthogonal to these directions.
\begin<<13838>>tex2html_deferred<<13838>>\par\end<<13839>>tex2html_deferred<<13839>>
In the figure below, the conjugate gradient method is compared with the gradient 
descent method for the case of \begin<<8020>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<8020>>$N=2$\end<<8021>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<8021>>. We see that the first search direction is
the same \begin<<8022>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<8022>>$-<<3306>>\begin<<13840>>tex2html_deferred<<13840>>\bf\end<<13841>>tex2html_deferred<<13841>>g<<3306>>_0$\end<<8023>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<8023>>\space for both methods. However, the next search direction 
\begin<<8024>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<8024>>$<<3307>>\begin<<13842>>tex2html_deferred<<13842>>\bf\end<<13843>>tex2html_deferred<<13843>>d<<3307>>_1$\end<<8025>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<8025>>\space is A-orthogonal to \begin<<8026>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<8026>>$<<3308>>\begin<<13844>>tex2html_deferred<<13844>>\bf\end<<13845>>tex2html_deferred<<13845>>d<<3308>>_0$\end<<8027>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<8027>>, same as the next error \begin<<8028>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<8028>>$<<3309>>\begin<<13846>>tex2html_deferred<<13846>>\bf\end<<13847>>tex2html_deferred<<13847>>e<<3309>>_1$\end<<8029>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<8029>>, 
different from the search direction \begin<<8030>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<8030>>$-<<3310>>\begin<<13848>>tex2html_deferred<<13848>>\bf\end<<13849>>tex2html_deferred<<13849>>g<<3310>>_1$\end<<8031>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<8031>>\space in gradient descent method. 
The conjugate gradient method finds the solution \begin<<8032>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<8032>>$<<3311>>\begin<<13850>>tex2html_deferred<<13850>>\bf\end<<13851>>tex2html_deferred<<13851>>x<<3311>>$\end<<8033>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<8033>>\space in \begin<<8034>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<8034>>$N=2$\end<<8035>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<8035>>\space steps, 
while the gradient descent method has to go through many more steps all 
orthogonal to each other before it finds the solution.
\begin<<13852>>tex2html_deferred<<13852>>\par\end<<13853>>tex2html_deferred<<13853>>
\htmladdimg<<3312>>figures/ConjugateGradient.png<<3312>>.
\begin<<13854>>tex2html_deferred<<13854>>\par\end<<13855>>tex2html_deferred<<13855>>
<<3313>>\begin<<13856>>tex2html_deferred<<13856>>\bf\end<<13857>>tex2html_deferred<<13857>>Find the A-orthogonal basis<<3313>>
\begin<<13858>>tex2html_deferred<<13858>>\par\end<<13859>>tex2html_deferred<<13859>>
The \begin<<8036>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<8036>>$N$\end<<8037>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<8037>>\space A-orthogonal search directions \begin<<8038>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<8038>>$\{<<3314>>\begin<<13860>>tex2html_deferred<<13860>>\bf\end<<13861>>tex2html_deferred<<13861>>d<<3314>>_0,\cdots,<<3315>>\begin<<13862>>tex2html_deferred<<13862>>\bf\end<<13863>>tex2html_deferred<<13863>>d<<3315>>_<<3316>>N-1<<3316>>\}$\end<<8039>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<8039>> 
can be constructed based on any set of \begin<<8040>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<8040>>$N$\end<<8041>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<8041>>\space independent vectors 
\begin<<8042>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<8042>>$\{<<3317>>\begin<<13864>>tex2html_deferred<<13864>>\bf\end<<13865>>tex2html_deferred<<13865>>v<<3317>>_0,\cdots,<<3318>>\begin<<13866>>tex2html_deferred<<13866>>\bf\end<<13867>>tex2html_deferred<<13867>>v<<3318>>_<<3319>>N-1<<3319>>\}$\end<<8043>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<8043>>\space by the 
\htmladdnormallink<<3320>>Gram-Schmidt process<<3320>><<3321>>../algebra/node2.html<<3321>>:
\begin<<3322>>equation<<3322>>
  <<3323>>\begin<<13868>>tex2html_deferred<<13868>>\bf\end<<13869>>tex2html_deferred<<13869>>d<<3323>>_n=<<3324>>\begin<<13870>>tex2html_deferred<<13870>>\bf\end<<13871>>tex2html_deferred<<13871>>v<<3324>>_n-\sum_<<3325>>j=0<<3325>>^<<3326>>n-1<<3326>> <<3327>>\begin<<13872>>tex2html_deferred<<13872>>\bf\end<<13873>>tex2html_deferred<<13873>>p<<3327>>_<<6702>><<3328>>\begin<<13874>>tex2html_deferred<<13874>>\bf\end<<13875>>tex2html_deferred<<13875>>d<<3328>>_j<<6702>>(<<3329>>\begin<<13876>>tex2html_deferred<<13876>>\bf\end<<13877>>tex2html_deferred<<13877>>v<<3329>>_n)
  =<<3330>>\begin<<13878>>tex2html_deferred<<13878>>\bf\end<<13879>>tex2html_deferred<<13879>>v<<3330>>_n-\sum_<<3331>>m=0<<3331>>^<<3332>>n-1<<3332>> \left(\frac<<6703>><<3333>>\begin<<13880>>tex2html_deferred<<13880>>\bf\end<<13881>>tex2html_deferred<<13881>>d<<3333>>^T_m<<3334>>\begin<<13882>>tex2html_deferred<<13882>>\bf\end<<13883>>tex2html_deferred<<13883>>A<<3334>><<3335>>\begin<<13884>>tex2html_deferred<<13884>>\bf\end<<13885>>tex2html_deferred<<13885>>v<<3335>>_n<<6703>><<6704>><<3336>>\begin<<13886>>tex2html_deferred<<13886>>\bf\end<<13887>>tex2html_deferred<<13887>>d<<3336>>^T_m<<3337>>\begin<<13888>>tex2html_deferred<<13888>>\bf\end<<13889>>tex2html_deferred<<13889>>A<<3337>><<3338>>\begin<<13890>>tex2html_deferred<<13890>>\bf\end<<13891>>tex2html_deferred<<13891>>d<<3338>>_m<<6704>>\right)  <<3339>>\begin<<13892>>tex2html_deferred<<13892>>\bf\end<<13893>>tex2html_deferred<<13893>>d<<3339>>_m
  =<<3340>>\begin<<13894>>tex2html_deferred<<13894>>\bf\end<<13895>>tex2html_deferred<<13895>>v<<3340>>_n-\sum_<<3341>>m=0<<3341>>^<<3342>>n-1<<3342>> \beta_<<3343>>nm<<3343>><<3344>>\begin<<13896>>tex2html_deferred<<13896>>\bf\end<<13897>>tex2html_deferred<<13897>>d<<3344>>_m
\end<<3345>>equation<<3345>>
where \begin<<8044>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<8044>>$\beta_<<3346>>nm<<3346>>=<<3347>>\begin<<13898>>tex2html_deferred<<13898>>\bf\end<<13899>>tex2html_deferred<<13899>>d<<3347>>^T_m<<3348>>\begin<<13900>>tex2html_deferred<<13900>>\bf\end<<13901>>tex2html_deferred<<13901>>A<<3348>><<3349>>\begin<<13902>>tex2html_deferred<<13902>>\bf\end<<13903>>tex2html_deferred<<13903>>v<<3349>>_n/(<<3350>>\begin<<13904>>tex2html_deferred<<13904>>\bf\end<<13905>>tex2html_deferred<<13905>>d<<3350>>^T_m<<3351>>\begin<<13906>>tex2html_deferred<<13906>>\bf\end<<13907>>tex2html_deferred<<13907>>A<<3351>><<3352>>\begin<<13908>>tex2html_deferred<<13908>>\bf\end<<13909>>tex2html_deferred<<13909>>d<<3352>>_m)$\end<<8045>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<8045>> 
and \begin<<8046>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<8046>>$\beta_<<3353>>nm<<3353>><<3354>>\begin<<13910>>tex2html_deferred<<13910>>\bf\end<<13911>>tex2html_deferred<<13911>>d<<3354>>_m$\end<<8047>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<8047>>\space is the A-projection of \begin<<8048>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<8048>>$<<3355>>\begin<<13912>>tex2html_deferred<<13912>>\bf\end<<13913>>tex2html_deferred<<13913>>v<<3355>>_n$\end<<8049>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<8049>>\space onto each
of the previous direction \begin<<8050>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<8050>>$<<3356>>\begin<<13914>>tex2html_deferred<<13914>>\bf\end<<13915>>tex2html_deferred<<13915>>d<<3356>>_m$\end<<8051>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<8051>>.
\begin<<13916>>tex2html_deferred<<13916>>\par\end<<13917>>tex2html_deferred<<13917>>
However, we specifically choose to use \begin<<8052>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<8052>>$<<3357>>\begin<<13918>>tex2html_deferred<<13918>>\bf\end<<13919>>tex2html_deferred<<13919>>v<<3357>>_n=-<<3358>>\begin<<13920>>tex2html_deferred<<13920>>\bf\end<<13921>>tex2html_deferred<<13921>>g<<3358>>_n$\end<<8053>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<8053>>, to gain
some significant computational advantage as shows below. Now the
Gram-Schmidt process above becomes:
\begin<<3359>>equation<<3359>>
  <<3360>>\begin<<13922>>tex2html_deferred<<13922>>\bf\end<<13923>>tex2html_deferred<<13923>>d<<3360>>_n =-<<3361>>\begin<<13924>>tex2html_deferred<<13924>>\bf\end<<13925>>tex2html_deferred<<13925>>g<<3361>>_n-\sum_<<3362>>m=0<<3362>>^<<3363>>n-1<<3363>> \beta_<<3364>>nm<<3364>><<3365>>\begin<<13926>>tex2html_deferred<<13926>>\bf\end<<13927>>tex2html_deferred<<13927>>d<<3365>>_m
  \label<<3366>>GSCG<<3366>>
\end<<3367>>equation<<3367>>
where
\begin<<3368>>equation<<3368>>
  \beta_<<3369>>nm<<3369>>=\frac<<6705>><<3370>>\begin<<13928>>tex2html_deferred<<13928>>\bf\end<<13929>>tex2html_deferred<<13929>>d<<3370>>_m^T<<3371>>\begin<<13930>>tex2html_deferred<<13930>>\bf\end<<13931>>tex2html_deferred<<13931>>A<<3371>><<3372>>\begin<<13932>>tex2html_deferred<<13932>>\bf\end<<13933>>tex2html_deferred<<13933>>v<<3372>>_n<<6705>><<6706>><<3373>>\begin<<13934>>tex2html_deferred<<13934>>\bf\end<<13935>>tex2html_deferred<<13935>>d<<3373>>^T_m<<3374>>\begin<<13936>>tex2html_deferred<<13936>>\bf\end<<13937>>tex2html_deferred<<13937>>A<<3374>><<3375>>\begin<<13938>>tex2html_deferred<<13938>>\bf\end<<13939>>tex2html_deferred<<13939>>d<<3375>>_m<<6706>>
  =-\frac<<6707>><<3376>>\begin<<13940>>tex2html_deferred<<13940>>\bf\end<<13941>>tex2html_deferred<<13941>>d<<3376>>_m^T<<3377>>\begin<<13942>>tex2html_deferred<<13942>>\bf\end<<13943>>tex2html_deferred<<13943>>A<<3377>><<3378>>\begin<<13944>>tex2html_deferred<<13944>>\bf\end<<13945>>tex2html_deferred<<13945>>g<<3378>>_n<<6707>><<6708>><<3379>>\begin<<13946>>tex2html_deferred<<13946>>\bf\end<<13947>>tex2html_deferred<<13947>>d<<3379>>^T_m<<3380>>\begin<<13948>>tex2html_deferred<<13948>>\bf\end<<13949>>tex2html_deferred<<13949>>A<<3380>><<3381>>\begin<<13950>>tex2html_deferred<<13950>>\bf\end<<13951>>tex2html_deferred<<13951>>d<<3381>>_m<<6708>>
  \;\;\;\;\;\;(m;SPMlt;n)
  \label<<3382>>GSbeta<<3382>>
\end<<3383>>equation<<3383>>
The equation above also indicates that \begin<<8054>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<8054>>$<<3384>>\begin<<13952>>tex2html_deferred<<13952>>\bf\end<<13953>>tex2html_deferred<<13953>>g<<3384>>_n$\end<<8055>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<8055>>\space can be written 
as a linear combination of all previous search directions
\begin<<8056>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<8056>>$<<3385>>\begin<<13954>>tex2html_deferred<<13954>>\bf\end<<13955>>tex2html_deferred<<13955>>d<<3385>>_0,\cdots,<<3386>>\begin<<13956>>tex2html_deferred<<13956>>\bf\end<<13957>>tex2html_deferred<<13957>>d<<3386>>_n$\end<<8057>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<8057>>:
\begin<<3387>>equation<<3387>>
  <<3388>>\begin<<13958>>tex2html_deferred<<13958>>\bf\end<<13959>>tex2html_deferred<<13959>>g<<3388>>_n=\sum_<<3389>>i=0<<3389>>^n \alpha_i<<3390>>\begin<<13960>>tex2html_deferred<<13960>>\bf\end<<13961>>tex2html_deferred<<13961>>d<<3390>>_i
\end<<3391>>equation<<3391>>
Premultiplying \begin<<8058>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<8058>>$<<3392>>\begin<<13962>>tex2html_deferred<<13962>>\bf\end<<13963>>tex2html_deferred<<13963>>g<<3392>>_<<3393>>n+1<<3393>>^T$\end<<8059>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<8059>>\space on both sides, we get
\begin<<3394>>equation<<3394>>
  <<3395>>\begin<<13964>>tex2html_deferred<<13964>>\bf\end<<13965>>tex2html_deferred<<13965>>g<<3395>>_<<3396>>n+1<<3396>>^T<<3397>>\begin<<13966>>tex2html_deferred<<13966>>\bf\end<<13967>>tex2html_deferred<<13967>>g<<3397>>_k=<<3398>>\begin<<13968>>tex2html_deferred<<13968>>\bf\end<<13969>>tex2html_deferred<<13969>>g<<3398>>_<<3399>>n+1<<3399>>^T\left( \sum_<<3400>>i=0<<3400>>^k \alpha_i<<3401>>\begin<<13970>>tex2html_deferred<<13970>>\bf\end<<13971>>tex2html_deferred<<13971>>d<<3401>>_i\right)
  =\sum_<<3402>>i=0<<3402>>^k \alpha_i\;<<3403>>\begin<<13972>>tex2html_deferred<<13972>>\bf\end<<13973>>tex2html_deferred<<13973>>g<<3403>>_<<3404>>n+1<<3404>>^T<<3405>>\begin<<13974>>tex2html_deferred<<13974>>\bf\end<<13975>>tex2html_deferred<<13975>>d<<3405>>_i=0
\end<<3406>>equation<<3406>>
The last equality is due to \begin<<8060>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<8060>>$<<3407>>\begin<<13976>>tex2html_deferred<<13976>>\bf\end<<13977>>tex2html_deferred<<13977>>g<<3407>>_<<3408>>n+1<<3408>>^T<<3409>>\begin<<13978>>tex2html_deferred<<13978>>\bf\end<<13979>>tex2html_deferred<<13979>>d<<3409>>_k=0$\end<<8061>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<8061>>\space (Eq. (\ref<<3410>>gd0<<3410>>)).
We see that \begin<<8062>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<8062>>$<<3411>>\begin<<13980>>tex2html_deferred<<13980>>\bf\end<<13981>>tex2html_deferred<<13981>>g<<3411>>_<<3412>>n+1<<3412>>$\end<<8063>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<8063>>\space is also orthogonal to all previous gradients 
\begin<<8064>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<8064>>$<<3413>>\begin<<13982>>tex2html_deferred<<13982>>\bf\end<<13983>>tex2html_deferred<<13983>>g<<3413>>_0,\cdots,<<3414>>\begin<<13984>>tex2html_deferred<<13984>>\bf\end<<13985>>tex2html_deferred<<13985>>g<<3414>>_n$\end<<8065>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<8065>>.
\begin<<13986>>tex2html_deferred<<13986>>\par\end<<13987>>tex2html_deferred<<13987>>
Pre-multiplying \begin<<8066>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<8066>>$<<3415>>\begin<<13988>>tex2html_deferred<<13988>>\bf\end<<13989>>tex2html_deferred<<13989>>g<<3415>>_k^T (k\ge n)$\end<<8067>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<8067>>\space on both sides of Eq. (\ref<<3416>>GSCG<<3416>>),
we get
\begin<<3417>>equation<<3417>> 
  <<3418>>\begin<<13990>>tex2html_deferred<<13990>>\bf\end<<13991>>tex2html_deferred<<13991>>g<<3418>>_k^T<<3419>>\begin<<13992>>tex2html_deferred<<13992>>\bf\end<<13993>>tex2html_deferred<<13993>>d<<3419>>_n=-<<3420>>\begin<<13994>>tex2html_deferred<<13994>>\bf\end<<13995>>tex2html_deferred<<13995>>g<<3420>>_k^T<<3421>>\begin<<13996>>tex2html_deferred<<13996>>\bf\end<<13997>>tex2html_deferred<<13997>>g<<3421>>_n-\sum_<<3422>>m=0<<3422>>^<<3423>>n-1<<3423>> \beta_<<3424>>mn<<3424>>\,<<3425>>\begin<<13998>>tex2html_deferred<<13998>>\bf\end<<13999>>tex2html_deferred<<13999>>g<<3425>>_k^T<<3426>>\begin<<14000>>tex2html_deferred<<14000>>\bf\end<<14001>>tex2html_deferred<<14001>>d<<3426>>_m
  =-<<3427>>\begin<<14002>>tex2html_deferred<<14002>>\bf\end<<14003>>tex2html_deferred<<14003>>g<<3427>>_k^T<<3428>>\begin<<14004>>tex2html_deferred<<14004>>\bf\end<<14005>>tex2html_deferred<<14005>>g<<3428>>_n
  =\left\{ \begin<<3429>>array<<3429>><<3430>>cc<<3430>>-||<<3431>>\begin<<14006>>tex2html_deferred<<14006>>\bf\end<<14007>>tex2html_deferred<<14007>>g<<3431>>_n||^2;SPMamp;n=k\\  0;SPMamp;n;SPMlt;k\end<<3432>>array<<3432>>\right.
