Note that all terms in the summation are zero as \begin<<8068>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<8068>>$<<3434>>\begin<<14008>>tex2html_deferred<<14008>>\bf\end<<14009>>tex2html_deferred<<14009>>g<<3434>>_k^T<<3435>>\begin<<14010>>tex2html_deferred<<14010>>\bf\end<<14011>>tex2html_deferred<<14011>>d<<3435>>_m=0$\end<<8069>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<8069>> 
