is symmetric as the Hessian matrices \begin<<9456>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<9456>>$<<5910>>\begin<<17108>>tex2html_deferred<<17108>>\bf\end<<17109>>tex2html_deferred<<17109>>H<<5910>>_f$\end<<9457>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<9457>>\space and \begin<<9458>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<9458>>$<<5911>>\begin<<17110>>tex2html_deferred<<17110>>\bf\end<<17111>>tex2html_deferred<<17111>>H<<5911>>_<<5912>>h_i<<5912>>,\;
