Combining this equation with the second one, we get an equation system 
of two vector variables \begin<<9474>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<9474>>$\delta<<6070>>\begin<<17340>>tex2html_deferred<<17340>>\bf\end<<17341>>tex2html_deferred<<17341>>x<<6070>>$\end<<9475>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<9475>>\space and \begin<<9476>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<9476>>$\delta<<6071>>\begin<<17342>>tex2html_deferred<<17342>>\bf\end<<17343>>tex2html_deferred<<17343>>\lambda<<6071>>$\end<<9477>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<9477>>\space with
