Solving this equation system we get \begin<<9478>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<9478>>$\delta<<6102>>\begin<<17380>>tex2html_deferred<<17380>>\bf\end<<17381>>tex2html_deferred<<17381>>x<<6102>>$\end<<9479>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<9479>>\space and \begin<<9480>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<9480>>$\delta<<6103>>\begin<<17382>>tex2html_deferred<<17382>>\bf\end<<17383>>tex2html_deferred<<17383>>\lambda<<6103>>$\end<<9481>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<9481>>,
and we can further find \begin<<9482>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<9482>>$\delta<<6104>>\begin<<17384>>tex2html_deferred<<17384>>\bf\end<<17385>>tex2html_deferred<<17385>>\mu<<6104>>$\end<<9483>>tex2html_wrap_inline<<9483>>\space by solving the third equation
\begin<<6105>>equation<<6105>>
  <<6106>>\begin<<17386>>tex2html_deferred<<17386>>\bf\end<<17387>>tex2html_deferred<<17387>>M<<6106>>\delta<<6107>>\begin<<17388>>tex2html_deferred<<17388>>\bf\end<<17389>>tex2html_deferred<<17389>>x<<6107>>+<<6108>>\begin<<17390>>tex2html_deferred<<17390>>\bf\end<<17391>>tex2html_deferred<<17391>>X<<6108>>\delta\mu=-<<6109>>\begin<<17392>>tex2html_deferred<<17392>>\bf\end<<17393>>tex2html_deferred<<17393>>XM1<<6109>>-<<6110>>\begin<<17394>>tex2html_deferred<<17394>>\bf\end<<17395>>tex2html_deferred<<17395>>1<<6110>>/t
