to get
\begin<<6112>>equation<<6112>>
  \delta<<6113>>\begin<<17396>>tex2html_deferred<<17396>>\bf\end<<17397>>tex2html_deferred<<17397>>\mu<<6113>>=<<6114>>\begin<<17398>>tex2html_deferred<<17398>>\bf\end<<17399>>tex2html_deferred<<17399>>X<<6114>>^<<6115>>-1<<6115>><<6116>>\begin<<17400>>tex2html_deferred<<17400>>\bf\end<<17401>>tex2html_deferred<<17401>>1<<6116>>/t-<<6117>>\begin<<17402>>tex2html_deferred<<17402>>\bf\end<<17403>>tex2html_deferred<<17403>>X<<6117>>^<<6118>>-1<<6118>><<6119>>\begin<<17404>>tex2html_deferred<<17404>>\bf\end<<17405>>tex2html_deferred<<17405>>M<<6119>>\delta<<6120>>\begin<<17406>>tex2html_deferred<<17406>>\bf\end<<17407>>tex2html_deferred<<17407>>x<<6120>>-<<6121>>\begin<<17408>>tex2html_deferred<<17408>>\bf\end<<17409>>tex2html_deferred<<17409>>\mu<<6121>>
